{"tid":863013,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"空氣污染好比溫水煮蛙","createTime":"2018-10-15T09:51:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-15T15:32:40.000Z","uid":34163,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"bd55bb300d0dff7ffd7be5df9a6239a01b012163","tid":863013,"uid":34163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T09:51:02.000Z","msg":"每日都會睇住個能見度同PM2.5數目<br />\n<br />\n夏天吹東南風 理論上應該吹海風 污染物較少<br />\n<br />\n之前幾年夏天都冇咩污染物 但係今年<br />\n夏天基本上能見度都唔高<br />\n<br />\n空氣污染唔再係中國專利<br />\n係影響曬全世界<br />\n<br />\n有人話個地球會自我修復<br />\n冇錯的確係 係自我修復緊<br />\n空氣污染引致既死亡人數按年上升<br />\n當空氣污染引致既死亡率高過出生率<br />\n存活人類減少<br />\n自然排放量會減低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n冬天來緊<br />\n大家又要活係一堆污染物之下<br />\n我屋企以前望到對面海座山（都幾遠下<br />\n我自己好似都慢慢習慣左望唔到座山<br />\n依家得較為好天既日子先會見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b603b4370b542d6136a56eaef047e2ed36bd8d6","tid":863013,"uid":34163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T09:52:15.000Z","msg":"不過都冇人理 馬照跑舞照跳功課繼續抄"},{"pid":"4f5239291f580b596763908a5ebabcd5eaed9e00","tid":863013,"uid":34163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T10:12:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e2c98d529ba4bc597c30d6765ab9547f97e8eef","tid":863013,"uid":34163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T10:13:06.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"cf0f5310835423b10cc168b46c907497c36c6787","tid":863013,"uid":34163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T10:13:16.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"f1b4472ac0291f270ee371c6587ee37843f82347","tid":863013,"uid":34163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T10:13:26.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"36b5abf1d1a38ac7e5999447a85521e973634b76","tid":863013,"uid":34163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T10:13:37.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"e424188109878b3fc3303a77d85d